headline: Peru Bets on Chevron and Riyadh to Jumpstart Its Energy Future
summary: Peru expects to sign in November an agreement with Saudi Arabia to develop lithium projects and other strategic minerals.

headline: How the Latest Oxy Deal and Analyst Views Are Reshaping the Company’s Valuation Story
summary: Occidental Petroleum’s stock narrative has shifted, highlighted by a recent uptick in its Fair Value Estimate from $51.00 to $51.55. This modest increase comes amid evolving market dynamics and reflects updated analyst sentiment.
